snippet.title: Super Mega Bread Trailer
snippet.description:
Bread Land is in trouble, and it's up to Bread Man to save the day!  Using butter to open doors, stop enemies, and fly over obstacles!

Get it here once it's out:
https://jclermont.itch.io/super-mega-bread

Coming soon, available September 20th 2017 for $1.

Made with Pico-8 and playable both through Pico-8 and web browsers.
